<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#1a56db">
<title>营销宣传 - 政企通</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',sans-serif;background:#f5f7fa;color:#1a1a2e}
.nav{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a56db,#1e40af);height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 24px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.nav a{color:#fff;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;font-weight:600}
.nav a:hover{opacity:.85}
.container{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;padding:60px 24px;text-align:center}
.icon{font-size:72px;margin-bottom:24px}
h1{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;color:#1a1a2e}
p{font-size:16px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.8;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto}
.coming-soon{display:inline-block;margin-top:30px;padding:10px 28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a56db,#2563eb);color:#fff;border-radius:24px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px}
.footer{text-align:center;padding:40px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="nav"><a href="index.html">&#8592; 返回首页</a></nav>
<div class="container">
<div class="icon">&#128640;</div>
<h1>营销宣传</h1>
<p>品牌策划、新媒体运营、广告投放、SEO优化等营销推广服务，即将上线。</p>
<div class="coming-soon">即 将 上 线</div>
</div>
<div class="footer">政企通 · 南通开发区企业一站式智慧服务平台</div>
</body>
</html>